ðŸ”¹ Basic Input Types
"text" -	A single-line text input.
"textarea" -	A multi-line text input.
"richtext" -	A rich text editor with formatting options.
"html" -	Allows raw HTML input.
"checkbox" -	A simple toggle (true/false).
"radio" -	A set of radio buttons (select one option).
"select" -	A dropdown menu to choose from multiple options.

ðŸŽ¨ Design & Styling Types
"color"	A color picker for selecting a single color.
"color_scheme"	Allows sections to use predefined color schemes.
"color_scheme_group"	Lets users create and manage multiple color schemes.

ðŸ”¤ Typography & Fonts
"font_picker"	Lets users select fonts from Shopifyâ€™s built-in fonts.
"range"	A slider to adjust font sizes or other numeric values.

ðŸ”„ Media & Images
"image_picker"	Allows users to upload or select an image.
"video"	Embeds a video.
"url"	Lets users input a URL.

ðŸ”§ Advanced & Custom Types
"blog"	Select a blog from the Shopify store.
"collection"	Select a product collection.
"product"	Select a single product.
"article"	Select a single blog article.
"page"	Select a page.
"link_list"	Select a menu from Shopify's navigation.
